A few coaches North Texas could turn to in its search for a new coach, with comments from Brett Vito:
Possible candidate Current position Kendal Briles Baylor offensive coordinator -- Would run wide-open offense, Big 12 Recruiter of Year in 2013-14 Doug Meacham TCU co-offensive coordinator -- Veteran coordinator, Texas native helps guide powerful TCU offense Mario Cristobal Alabama offensive line coach -- Turned around a terrible Florida Int'l team, has won at a mid-major Major Applewhite Houston offensive coordinator -- A celebrity across Texas who has worked at Rice, Texas, Houston Jake Spavital Texas A&M offensive coordinator -- Worked at Oklahoma State, Houston, coached Johnny Manziel Brad Smiley Trinity Valley CC head coach -- 2014 Nat'l Junior College Coach of Year has Texas ties, is Baylor grad On Twitter:
 @brettvito
